---
title: Cheesy Pork, Creamy Spinach & Green Beans with Roasted Potato Chunks & Garlic Veggies
description: We've turbo-charged your pork tonight! Special additions like a too-good-to-be-true cheesy and creamy spinach sauce, herbed spices on the golden chunks of potato and a robust side of veggies are what it's all about. Happy days indeed!
